_sText: Map by Timo and Marco. ___________________ Info - 7 Bombsites - 7 Hostages - Many Weapons - Many Camping positions - Many objects to hide - Many burnable things - A Secret Place in the Air - Much fun Size: 11,1MB ___________________ Why i made this map I made this map, because i wanted to have a map with many fun things, like burning houses, a secret place and many Bomb Sites. So i started without knowing what i want to do. I just created a street, some grass and houses. I added Bomb Sites and Secret Places. The map went bigger and bigger. Until i decided to release it.
